These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, bellflower
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, blood-red
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, bongani
2 different pets are kept: ferret, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, van
1. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
4. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | milk       | mirinda    |
| Flower           | bellflower | daisy |
| Color   | blood-red     | black   |
| Cigar   | bongani  | havana     |
| Pet           | goat       | ferret     |
| Transport     | roller     | van        |

