.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, daisy
House: ranch-style, farmhouse
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, crime
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon
2 different pets are kept: bird, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Flower      | begonia        | daisy   |
| House         | farmhouse | ranch-style |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | crime   |
| Game   | mah-jongg       | backgammon     |
| Pet           | rat        | bird    |
| Transport     | motorbike  | ship    |

