4. the person traveling to marseilles is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |
| Sport      | biathlon    | baseball      |
| Game          | snooker | mah-jongg |
| City           | edinburgh     | marseilles      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | disco       |
| Pet           | snake     | ferret      |
| Transport     | scooter   | bus         |

 